        "name": "Sneak Attack",
        "type": "scaling",
        "description": {
          "summary": "Deal extra damage when attacking vulnerable targets.",
          "fullText": "The assassin gains sneak attack damage. This extra damage applies when the target is denied its Dexterity bonus to AC or when the assassin flanks the target, following normal sneak attack rules."
